snippet.title: Amber Heard's deposition from 2016: 'They said that I looked hurt'
snippet.description:
Actor Amber Heard gives evidence in a deposition from August 2016.

When questioned, Heard speaks about an incident in which police officers were called to her house in May 2016.

The clip was played in court during the libel case between Johnny Depp and publishers of The Sun newspaper.
